profile: Locally owned & operated Whitby Garage Doors Ltd. is a division of Markham Garage Doors Ltd. who has been redefining the garage door industry with customer care that is second to none and a desire to give the customer the best possible buying experience. Whitby is no exception to this philosophy it has been built to give the same level of service to the Durham Region as York Region has enjoyed for over 10 years. Owners Chris Dale and Kevin Chappel have created a new division of their company due to overwhelming interest in the Durham Region that has been filled to date by Markham Garage Doors Ltd. Now Brandon Sloan a highly skilled technician of Markham Garage Doors Ltd. has become the roots for Whitby Garage Doors Ltd. Brandon is not only one of the best technicians’ we have come to know in the industry, he enjoys customer interaction, providing the best in service and value, and lives locally in the Durham Region. Brandon has been an integral part of Markham Garage Doors Ltd since its inception and will be very successful in providing customers with a level of service that they have not experienced in the past. Whitby Garage Doors and Markham Garage Doors share the very same ideal, that is to ensure our customers receive the best service, on time every time. Enhance your Curb Appeal with Whitby Garage Doors Ltd.
service_area: Whitby, Brooklin, Pickering, Oshawa, Ajax, Bomanville, Courtice, Stouffville, Uxbridge, and the surrounding areas.
hours: Monday to Friday 7:30 am to 5:00 pm
products: Whitby Garage Doors is your complete Garage Door Store.  We Service all makes and models of garage doors and openers.  We also sell that latest and greatest products in the garage door industry.  Everything you need from repairs to new garage doors to openers we have it all.  We live, support, and work in the Durham area.  You will see our well signed vehicles within the Durham Region. If your looking for an honest trustworthy company please call us today for fast friendly service.
services: Whitby Garage Doors is able to service just about any garage door or opener problem you may encounter.  Our service vehicles have nearly every part you may require on board.  If we can't fix it the part no longer exists.  Give us a call for same day service and fair prices.

profile: Upright Door Service Inc. is a family run residential garage door service company with over 25 years of experience. We provide fast, dependable service & quality workmanship to all of our clients. Our service vehicles are well stocked, and our qualified technicians are able to complete most repairs on the spot. When new product is needed we offer competitively priced and superior quality garage doors and operators. Alan Fortnum, the owner/operator of Upright Door Service Inc. has been involved in the garage door industry since 1985 (DBA Adal Carpentry 1985-2000). January 2001, the name was changed to Upright Door Service in order to better reflect the nature of our business and to allow us to better focus on the needs of our garage door clients. Since it's inception, Upright Door Service Inc. has been a proud member of the International Door Association (IDA). Alan, and brother Jim Fortnum were among the first in Durham Region to be recognized as Certified Residential Door System Technicians by the IDA.
